membership:
ORMAZABAL is member of several electrical and electromechanical associations, federations and confederations both at local level (in several Member States) and at European level.&#xd;
&#xd;
As an example, ORMAZABAL is active member in AFBEL and CONFEMETAL (Spain), ZVEI (Germany), GIMELEC (France), T&amp;D EUROPE, ORGALIME (EU), BusinessEurope etc.&#xd;
&#xd;
The aim of ORMAZABAL membership in all those organizations is to collaborate in the impulse of the development of the present and future electrical infrastructures (i.e. Smart Grids)
